OL,3,CAnti-Muslim hate definition reportedly
OL,4,Crehashed amid free speech concerns
OL,6,FThe wording of an official definition
OL,7,Fof Islamophobia has been rehashed,
OL,8,Famid concerns about the impact it
OL,9,Fcould have on free speech, according
OL,10,Fto reports.
OL,12,FA Government working group will aim to
OL,13,Ffocus on defining "anti-Muslim hate"
OL,14,Finstead of Islamophobia, according to
OL,15,Fthe Telegraph.
OL,17,FCritics of the efforts to create a new
OL,18,Flegal definition for Islamophobia had
OL,19,Fraised concerns that doing so could
OL,20,Fcreate backdoor blasphemy laws, and
OL,21,Fcurtail speech about Islamic extremism.
