OL,3,CAnti-Muslim hate definition reportedly
OL,4,Crehashed amid free speech concerns
OL,6,FMinisters launched the working group
OL,7,Faimed at defining Islamophobia or anti-
OL,8,FMuslim hatred in February, in an
OL,9,Feffort to help stem rising numbers of
OL,10,Fhate crimes against Muslims.
OL,12,FThe review of the definition, led by
OL,13,Fformer Conservative minister Dominic
OL,14,FGrieve, is said to have moved away
OL,15,Ffrom using the words "Islamophobia"
OL,16,Fand "Muslimness", according to the
OL,17,FTelegraph.
OL,19,FNew wording will aim to define hatred
OL,20,Ftowards Muslims, but also protect free
OL,21,Fspeech, the newspaper said.
