OL,3,CAnti-Muslim hate definition reportedly
OL,4,Crehashed amid free speech concerns
OL,6,FCrossbench peer Baroness Gohir, one of
OL,7,Fthe experts on the working group, told
OL,8,Fthe newspaper she expected the public
OL,9,Fto be "pleasantly surprised" when the
OL,10,Freview concludes.
OL,12,FLady Gohir, who is also chief
OL,13,Fexecutive of the Muslim Women's
OL,14,FNetwork UK, added: "I expect those who
OL,15,Fopposed the already existing
OL,16,Fdefinitions for being too vague, or
OL,17,Fbecause they felt these prevented
OL,18,Fcriticism of Islam or debate of other
OL,19,Fissues of concern to them, will want
OL,20,Fministers to adopt ours, as I believe
OL,21,Fit resolves those concerns."
