OL,6,FShe also warned that if the group's
OL,7,Fwording is not adopted, the current
OL,8,F"problematic" definition will continue
OL,9,Fto be used.
OL,11,FA spokesman for the Ministry of
OL,12,FHousing, Communities and Local
OL,13,FGovernment said it did not comment on
OL,14,Fleaks and was considering the working
OL,15,Fgroup's recommendations.
OL,17,FWhen the working group was launched at
OL,18,Fthe end of February, it said it aimed
OL,19,Fto deliver a new definition within six
OL,20,Fmonths.
